<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='605:641'>　　後交者四<span class='krp-note'>坎坤成師比/頥坤成謙豫</span>　<span class='krp-note'>乾坤成否泰觀/大過坤成臨</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='641:644'>坎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='644:676'>　　先交者三<span class='krp-note'>坎坤成師比過坎中孚成/困井  坎大  成渙節</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='676:714'>　　後交者四<span class='krp-note'>小過坎成屯䝉離乾坎成需訟濟/頤坎成蹇解    坎成既濟未</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='714:717'>離</span>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='717:762'>　　先交者五<span class='krp-note'>離乾成同人大有/  離中孚成革鼎</span>　<span class='krp-note'>離大過成家人暌/離頥成豐旅  離</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='762:779'>　　　　　　<span class='krp-note'>坎成既/濟未濟</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='779:805'>　　後交者二<span class='krp-note'>小過離成噬嗑賁/  坤離成晉明夷</span></span>
