<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='921:939'>　　先交者一<span class='krp-note'>中孚大過/成㢲兊</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='939:982'>　　後交者六<span class='krp-note'>小過中孚成隨蠱中頥中孚成咸恒中/乾中孚成姤  坤  孚成革升  坎</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='982:1003'>　　　　　　<span class='krp-note'>孚成坤井鼎離/中孚成革</span></span>
