<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1123:1147'>　　先交者二<span class='krp-note'>大過坤成臨觀益/大過小過成損</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1147:1191'>　　後交者五<span class='krp-note'>乾大過成小畜履妹離大過成家人暌/  頥大過成漸歸    中孚大過成㢲</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1191:1211'>　　　　　　<span class='krp-note'>兊成坎大/過  渙節</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1211:1237'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0057', 'WYG', '003-3b' );" name="003-3b" class="pb">[003-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
